1. On je *šampion* u plivanju. (He is a *champion* in swimming.)
2. Naš tim je osvojio titulu *šampiona*. (Our team won the title of *champions*.)
3. Danas će biti proglašen novi *šampion*. (Today a new *champion* will be announced.)
4. Ovaj *šampion* je već osvojio tri uzastopne titule. (This *champion* has already won three consecutive titles.)
5. Da bi postao *šampion*, moraš da treniraš naporno. (To become a *champion*, you have to train hard.)
6. Koliko puta je Novak Đoković bio *šampion* na Vimbldonu? (How many times has Novak Djokovic been *champion* at Wimbledon?)
7. Naš *šampion* se povredio tokom utakmice. (Our *champion* got injured during the game.)
8. Bila sam jako srećna kada sam videla da je moj omiljeni tim postao *šampion*. (I was very happy when I saw that my favorite team became *champions*.)
9. U ovoj kategoriji, *šampionat* je veoma neizvestan. (In this category, the *championship* is very unpredictable.)
10. Svi igrači su srećni kada osvoje titulu *šampiona*. (All players are happy when they win the *champion* title.)